{"title":"vue 后记","date":"2019-01-25T07:56:38.000Z","slug":"vue-2","tags":["vue"],"categories":["vue"],"updated":"2019-01-26T10:04:46.993Z","content":"<h2 id=\"Vue-extend构造器\"><a href=\"#Vue-extend构造器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Vue.extend构造器\"></a>Vue.extend构造器</h2><blockquote>\n<p>vue.extend（构造器）类似于组件,data选项是特例,创建完成之后使用<code>$mount()</code>挂载到标签上</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"Vue-filter过滤器\"><a href=\"#Vue-filter过滤器\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Vue.filter过滤器\"></a>Vue.filter过滤器</h2><blockquote>\n<p>用在<code>v-bind</code>中或者<code>花括号中</code>,写在尾部用管道符隔开<code>|</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>一个组件的 <code>data</code> 选项必须是一个<code>函数</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"Vue-compile渲染函数\"><a href=\"#Vue-compile渲染函数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Vue.compile渲染函数\"></a>Vue.compile渲染函数</h2><blockquote>\n<p>相当于在当前实例上渲染一个dom的结构,当这个实例的el属性挂载到标签上的时候就会渲染这个dom结构<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">var res = Vue.compile(&apos;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span&gt;&#123;&#123; msg &#125;&#125;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&apos;)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">new Vue(&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  data: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    msg: &apos;hello&apos;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  render: res.render,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  staticRenderFns: res.staticRenderFns</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n</blockquote>\n","next":{"title":"vue-axios","slug":"vue-axios"},"link":"http://yoursite.com/post/vue-2/","toc":[{"title":"Vue.extend构造器","id":"Vue-extend构造器","index":"1"},{"title":"Vue.filter过滤器","id":"Vue-filter过滤器","index":"2"},{"title":"Vue.compile渲染函数","id":"Vue-compile渲染函数","index":"3"}]}